 "remarks": "Privately tucked away at the end of a long circular drive on 6+ acres, this exceptional country estate blends timeless elegance with the warmth and comfort of everyday living. Though grand in scale, the home feels intimate and inviting, designed for both relaxed living and memorable entertaining. Exquisite architectural details, a covered mahogany veranda, sunroom, library, and exceptional kitchen/great room create spaces that are both sophisticated and welcoming.The current owners have further elevated the property with extensive professional landscaping, creating a breathtaking natural setting anchored by a gorgeous pool and spa. The lifestyle here is truly special with effortless access to all schools, making daily routines remarkably convenient. Outdoors, the property becomes a year-round retreat; from winter sledding on the gentle hill to summer slip-and-slides, exploring the brook in rain boots, and evenings filled with birdsong and visits from owls among the beautifully tended grounds. A luxurious primary suite, private bedroom wing, and walk-out finished lower level complete this extraordinary retreat where privacy, nature, and refined living come together in a setting that feels a world away, yet close to everything.",
